name: Analyze That
description: Mobster Paul Vitti is released into Dr. Ben Sobol's care, where only more chaos ensues.

review.author: mattkratz
review.heading: Less good
review.reviewBody: Sequels rarely live up to the original, and this is no exception. It has its moments, as well as some laughs, but the original was better and funnier. I sort of liked it, but as I said... You might like it if you liked the original. ** out of ****
